{"article_id":"CrcXuDtPPagmX4xZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sessions recuses himself from Trump-Russia probe","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The attorney general is removing himself","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"following reports","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"he met twice with the Russian ambassador during Trump 's campaign .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions announced Thursday","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that he will recuse himself from any investigations","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"related to campaigns for president ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"including any probe into contacts between President Donald Trump ' s campaign and Russian officials .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"\" I have recused myself in the matters","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that deal with the Trump campaign , \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Sessions told reporters Thursday at a news conference at the Justice Department .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Sessions ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who maintained support from Trump himself ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"he consulted senior Justice Department staff for their \" candid and honest opinion","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"about what I should do . \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" My staff recommended recusal , \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"\" They said","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"since I had involvement with the campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"I should not be involved in any campaign investigation .","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"I have studied the rules","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and considered their comments and evaluation .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"I believe","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"those recommendations are right and just . \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"In a statement","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"following his remarks ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Sessions noted","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that his recusal goes for \" any existing or future investigations of any matters","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"related in any way to the campaign for president of the United States . \"","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"He added , however ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"\" This announcement should not be interpreted as confirmation of the existence of any investigation or suggestive of the scope of any such investigation . \"","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"A growing number of Republicans had called on Sessions to recuse himself","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- and Democratic leaders had insisted","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he resign altogether -","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"after reports emerged Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that Sessions had met twice with the Russian ambassador last year","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"despite testifying during his confirmation hearing","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that he had no communications with Russians during the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"amplifying the Trump administration ' s Russia problem .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"In an interview with Tucker Carlson on Fox News on Thursday evening , Sessions said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that in the coming days he plans to to file a supplement to the Senate record","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"to clarify","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that he did meet with the Russian ambassador .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" I will definitely make that a part of the record , \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"While talking with Carlson ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he didn ' t recall much specific about his conversation with the ambassador , apart from a disagreement about Ukraine policy .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"they didn ' t discuss the presidential campaign in a \" meaningful way . \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Trump himself offered his support via a statement","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"released later on Thursday night ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"the attorney general `` did not say anything wrong . ''","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"`` He could have stated his response more accurately ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"but it was clearly not intentional , ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Trump continued ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"before blasting Democrats for `` overplaying their hand , ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"and decrying the `` illegal leaks of classified and other information . ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Sessions insisted Thursday","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that his statements at the hearing were \" honest and correct \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"because his contacts with Russian Ambassador Sergey Kislyak were not related to the campaign","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"but to official matters","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"related to his service as a member of the Senate Armed Services Committee .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"The attorney general , however ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"who was until three weeks ago a U.S. senator from Alabama ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"he could not rule out the possibility","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"the campaign came up","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"when the Russian diplomat visited Sessions ' Capitol Hill office in September .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"\" I don ' t recall , \"","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Sessions told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"\" Most of these ambassadors are pretty gossipy","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and this was in the campaign season ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"but I don ' t recall any specific political discussions . \"","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Sessions said","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"his memories of the discussion were somewhat vague ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"although he suggested","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"there was little chance of skullduggery","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"because of the presence of two staffers from his office at the meeting .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"The pair are retired Army colonels ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he noted .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Sessions said","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"he remembered Kislyak being \" pretty much of an old-style Soviet-type ambassador \"","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"and denying any Russian wrongdoing in Ukraine .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"The exchange ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"he said ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"grew somewhat tense","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"after Kislyak blamed the unrest in Ukraine on \" everyone else . \"","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"\" It got to be a little bit of a testy conversation at that point , \"","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Sessions said","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"he was preparing to send the Senate Judiciary Committee a letter","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"clarifying his answers on Russia .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"he regretted not mentioning the meetings .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"\" In retrospect , I should have slowed down","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and said ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"' But I did meet one Russian official a couple of times , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"the attorney general added .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"After riding high on Trump ' s well-received first address to Congress on Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"the White House found itself mired once again in the scandal","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"over whether Trump campaign officials had frequent contact with Russian officials last year ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"as officials from President Barack Obama ' s administration were looking into allegations","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that the Russian government was engaging in cyberattacks","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"to try to tilt the election Trump ' s way .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Calls","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"for Sessions to recuse himself from the Justice Department ' s investigation into ties between Trump and Russia","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"had snowballed ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"following a Washington Post report Wednesday night","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"exposing multiple meetings between Sessions and Kislyak during the campaign .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Those meetings ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"one of which occurred during the Republican National Convention in Cleveland ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"came amid an alleged effort by Russia","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"to aid Trump ' s campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"for which Sessions was a prominent surrogate .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"During a Thursday afternoon tour of an aircraft carrier in Newport News , Virginia , Trump responded to a reporter 's shouted question ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"that he had \" total \" confidence in Sessions .","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"Asked if he knew about Sessions ' conversations with the Russian ambassador ,","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"\" I was n't aware , \"","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"and asked","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"if Sessions should recuse himself ,","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"the president responded ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"\" I don ' t think so . \"","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"Sessions did not disclose his meetings with the ambassador","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"when asked about connections between the Kremlin and the Trump campaign during his confirmation hearings .","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"In fact , he told Sen. Al Franken","depth":16},{"id":131,"text":"( D-Minn. )","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"that \" I did not have communications with the Russians. \"","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"In a set of written answers for Sen. Patrick Leahy","depth":17},{"id":134,"text":"( D-Vt. ) ,","depth":17},{"id":135,"text":"Sessions said","depth":16},{"id":136,"text":"he had not been in contact with Russian officials","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"regarding the 2016 campaign .","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"Aboard the aircraft carrier , Trump said","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Sessions \" probably did \" tell the truth in his testimony to Franken and Leahy .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"\" This is the latest attack against the Trump administration by partisan Democrats .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"[ Attorney ] General Sessions met with the ambassador in an official capacity as a member of the Senate Armed Services Committee ,","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"which is entirely consistent with his testimony , \"","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"a White House official said .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"\" It ' s no surprise","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Sen. Al Franken is pushing this story","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"immediately following President Trump 's successful address to the nation . \"","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"In an interview with Fox News , White House press secretary Sean Spicer said","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"Sessions \" did his job \"","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"and had been \" 100 percent straight \" with the Senate Judiciary Committee during his confirmation hearings .","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"He said","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"Democrats were guilty of \" continuing to push a false narrative for political purposes . \"","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"\" Look , there ' s nothing","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"to recuse himself [ from ] , \"","depth":16},{"id":154,"text":"Spicer added .","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"\" He was 100 percent straight with the committee ,","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"and I think","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"that people","depth":18},{"id":158,"text":"who are choosing to play partisan politics with this","depth":18},{"id":159,"text":"should be ashamed of themselves . \"","depth":17},{"id":160,"text":"When Sessions was asked why he recused himself","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"despite Trump and Spicer saying","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"he should not ,","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"the attorney general said","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"they were not familiar with the ethics standards","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"involved .","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"\" I feel like","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"they don ' t know the rules , the ethics rules .","depth":16},{"id":168,"text":"Most people don ' t , \"","depth":16},{"id":169,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"\" But","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"when you evaluate the rules ,","depth":16},{"id":172,"text":"I feel like ...","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"I should not be involved investigating a campaign","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"I had a role in . \"","depth":15},{"id":175,"text":"A spokeswoman for Russia 's foreign ministry ,","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"speaking to CNN on Thursday morning ,","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"Kislyak is a \" world-class diplomat \"","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"who has \" communicated with his American colleagues through decades on different fields. \"","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"CNN had accused Kislyak of being a Russian spy","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"and warned the network to \" stop spreading lie [ s ] and false news \"","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"as she walked away from her interviewer .","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"In a brief exchange Thursday morning with a reporter from NBC News , Sessions himself had said","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"he would recuse himself","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"\" whenever it ' s appropriate \"","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"but denied","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"that he had discussed the campaign with Russian officials .","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"\" I have not met with any Russians at any time","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"to discuss any political campaign ,","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"and those remarks are unbelievable to me","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"and are false , \"","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"But a senior national security official from the Obama administration said","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"ties between Trump and Russia were a source of grave concern for the outgoing administration in its final days .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"The official said","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"he had no specific information","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"that Sessions was among those","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"interfacing with the Kremlin on behalf of the incoming administration ,","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"but he said","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"former national security adviser Michael Flynn ,","depth":16},{"id":202,"text":"who was forced to resign over misstatements to Vice President Mike Pence and others about conversations with the Russian ambassador ,","depth":16},{"id":203,"text":"was not acting alone .","depth":15},{"id":204,"text":"\" It seems pretty clear that","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"[ Flynn ] was not a rogue here , \"","depth":14},{"id":206,"text":"the senior official said .","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"\" I don ' t believe","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"that Flynn was the only person","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"promising things to the Russians ,","depth":15},{"id":210,"text":"communicating to them","depth":16},{"id":211,"text":"what would happen","depth":17},{"id":212,"text":"once the Trump administration came in . \"","depth":17},{"id":213,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"( D-Calif. ) ,","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"the ranking member on the House Intelligence Committee ,","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"on Thursday called for Sessions to step down ,","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"the senator had not met `` his own rigorous standard '' for `` complete and truthful testimony . ''","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"Schiff complained earlier Thursday","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"following a briefing by FBI Director James Comey","depth":14},{"id":221,"text":"that the bureau was withholding information","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"regarding its probe into the Kremlin ' s efforts","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"to interfere in last year ' s election .","depth":15},{"id":224,"text":"\" I would say","depth":14},{"id":225,"text":"at this point we know less than a fraction of what the FBI knows , \"","depth":14},{"id":226,"text":"Schiff told reporters","depth":14},{"id":227,"text":"following the briefing .","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"\" I appreciate","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"we had a long briefing and testimony from the director today ,","depth":13},{"id":230,"text":"but","depth":13},{"id":231,"text":"in order for us to do our investigation in a thorough and credible way ,","depth":14},{"id":232,"text":"we 're gon na need the FBI to fully cooperate ,","depth":15},{"id":233,"text":"to be willing to tell us the length and breadth of any counterintelligence investigations","depth":16},{"id":234,"text":"they are conducting . \"","depth":16},{"id":235,"text":"As the furor over Sessions grew ,","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"about 150 people gathered outside the Justice Department","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"to demanded","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"that he step down .","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"\" Lock him up !","depth":12},{"id":240,"text":"Perjury is a crime .","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"Sessions resign ! \"","depth":13},{"id":242,"text":"protesters chanted .","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"Those","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"turning out","depth":14},{"id":245,"text":"to call for Sessions ' exit","depth":14},{"id":246,"text":"heard from several Democratic lawmakers ,","depth":13},{"id":247,"text":"including Reps. Nydia Velazquez , Eleanor Holmes Norton and Sheila Jackson Lee .","depth":13},{"id":248,"text":"The demonstrators cheered","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"as Lee said , incorrectly ,","depth":14},{"id":250,"text":"that House Speaker Paul Ryan had just called on Sessions to recuse himself from the probe into alleged Russian tampering with the U.S. election .","depth":14},{"id":251,"text":"\" Not enough , \"","depth":15},{"id":252,"text":"Lee declared .","depth":15},{"id":253,"text":"\" We will be sending a letter to president Trump","depth":15},{"id":254,"text":"asking him to seek the resignation of his attorney general","depth":16},{"id":255,"text":"or fire him right on the spot . \"","depth":16},{"id":256,"text":"Even after Sessions announced his recusal ,","depth":12},{"id":257,"text":"it wasn ' t enough for House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":13},{"id":258,"text":"who accused him of perjury","depth":15},{"id":259,"text":"while calling for his resignation .","depth":15},{"id":260,"text":"His \" narrow recusal and his sorry attempt","depth":18},{"id":261,"text":"to explain away his perjury","depth":18},{"id":262,"text":"are totally inadequate , \"","depth":17},{"id":263,"text":"she said a statement .","depth":16},{"id":264,"text":"\" Attorney General Sessions ' lies to the Senate and to the American people make him unfit to serve as the chief law enforcement officer of our country .","depth":16},{"id":265,"text":"He must resign immediately . \"","depth":16},{"id":266,"text":"Republicans , in contrast , scoffed at the idea of a resignation .","depth":13},{"id":267,"text":"Chuck Grassley , an Iowa Republican","depth":18},{"id":268,"text":"who chairs the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":18},{"id":269,"text":"said","depth":17},{"id":270,"text":"he had recommended recusal to Sessions earlier Thursday .","depth":16},{"id":271,"text":"\" First and foremost , any talk of resignation is nonsense , \"","depth":16},{"id":272,"text":"Grassley said in a statement .","depth":16},{"id":273,"text":"\" There ' s little doubt","depth":16},{"id":274,"text":"that alleged conflicts ,","depth":20},{"id":275,"text":"no matter how flimsy","depth":20},{"id":276,"text":"and regardless of whether or not they are based in fact ,","depth":19},{"id":277,"text":"will be used against him","depth":18},{"id":278,"text":"to discredit him and any potential investigation into alleged conversations between the campaign and the Russian government .","depth":17},{"id":279,"text":"So , his actions today were the right thing","depth":16},{"id":280,"text":"to do . \"","depth":16},{"id":281,"text":"At a press conference Thursday morning , Ryan had said","depth":14},{"id":282,"text":"Sessions need not recuse himself","depth":15},{"id":283,"text":"unless he becomes the subject of an investigation ,","depth":16},{"id":284,"text":"at which point the attorney general would \" of course \" step aside .","depth":16},{"id":285,"text":"The speaker said","depth":14},{"id":286,"text":"he had seen no evidence","depth":15},{"id":287,"text":"that the Trump campaign colluded with Russian government officials during the 2016 campaign .","depth":15},{"id":288,"text":"Democrats on the House Judiciary Committee sent a letter Thursday to Comey , the FBI director , and U.S. Attorney Channing Phillips ,","depth":11},{"id":289,"text":"seeking a criminal investigation into Sessions .","depth":11},{"id":290,"text":"The letter ,","depth":14},{"id":291,"text":"signed by every Democrat on the panel ,","depth":14},{"id":292,"text":"suggested","depth":13},{"id":293,"text":"Sessions may have been in violation of perjury and lying to Congress laws","depth":12},{"id":294,"text":"and asked the FBI for a briefing on its investigation into the Trump campaign ' s alleged ties to Russia .","depth":11},{"id":295,"text":"The Democrats said","depth":10},{"id":296,"text":"Sessions ' rationales","depth":13},{"id":297,"text":"for meeting Kislyak","depth":13},{"id":298,"text":"\" appear to be disingenuous at best","depth":12},{"id":299,"text":"as the questions","depth":13},{"id":300,"text":"put to him","depth":13},{"id":301,"text":"did not in any way ask","depth":13},{"id":302,"text":"if the meeting was campaign related . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":605,"left":0,"right":604,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":604,"left":305,"right":603,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":1,"right":304,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":603,"left":333,"right":602,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":333,"left":326,"right":332,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":326,"left":311,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":308,"right":310,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":4,"right":307,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":306,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":309,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":313,"right":324,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":313,"left":312,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":312,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":314,"right":323,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":314,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":319,"right":322,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":319,"left":315,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":18,"right":317,"re